{"tid":1504729,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十六計第二策–圍魏救趙","createTime":"2019-08-25T11:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T11:33:35.000Z","uid":147787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7b462c7ce8519852f609a77389fb73125f8ddc24","tid":1504729,"uid":147787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:28:36.000Z","msg":"三十六計大家聽得多，然而大家又知唔知有邊三十六計呢？今日我會同大家介紹其中一策，依一策稱之為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">圍魏救趙</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所謂<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">圍魏救趙</span></span></strong>，就要追尋到公元前三五三年，魏國重兵包圍了趙國首都邯鄲，趙國慌忙向齊國求救。齊國大將田忌準備率軍趕去趙國，他的謀士孫臏勸阻說：「要解開雜亂糾紛，不能握拳不放；要魏軍全力攻趙，精兵銳卒勢必傾巢出動，國內一定只剩下老弱兵丁。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將軍不如輕裝疾奔魏都大梁，占據險要，擊其虛處。敵人必然放開趙國，回兵自救</span></span></strong>，這樣，我們便能<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一舉解開邯鄲之圍</span></span></strong>，又可乘魏軍疲憊之際，一鼓殲之。」 <br />\n<br />\n簡單啲咁講返，內容係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">先退到敵人虛弱嘅後方，再襯敵方精銳部隊攻打另一敵人時，趁機會打敵方。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中學果陣聽教歷史既老師講過，依招<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">20:00</span></span></strong>用，效果更佳。"},{"pid":"23f4438f0b76507e6af6e380095b8cfa9c7d3927","tid":1504729,"uid":147787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:28:47.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"8453bd7d497aaff63764a037548e4e1d99c55481","tid":1504729,"uid":147787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"d39373733fa18e16d88ea7ec4acc8a863c9e3a7e","tid":1504729,"uid":147787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:29:09.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"c7cb50bb8f5ae1384b3f037ac8088d75e996686f","tid":1504729,"uid":147787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:29:19.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"47a5232e719ed